name: Frida Punk 097 - FRIxDIEGO
description:
Frida Kahlo X Diego Rivera

An Artist in love with another Artist.
So much in love they married twice. There was much Frida had to say about her love of Diego.

“Sometimes, Diego himself would pass by, and we would tease him. One day, they asked me who I wanted to marry, and I said I would not marry, but I did want to have a child by Diego Rivera.” - Frida Kahlo
